curam.util.xml.intf

Interface XSLTemplateUtility

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    curam.util.xml.base.XSLTemplateUtility, XSLTemplateUtility, XSLTemplateUtilityFactory

    public interface XSLTemplateUtility
    Utility functions useful when selecting templates for printing documents. (This is assigned to the dummy server to force the SDE to build the BOL library.)
